The Brotherhood of the Rogues was just recently formed in 2013. The Rogues
are a very quiet bunch that obsess over the shadows and the many
things they can do within them. They are the masters of surprise attacks
and will do anything to benefit themselves.

If you are interested in becoming One with the Shadows, you
should seek a Rogue that is at least 19+30 and ask them
to introduce them to the Brotherhood.
